<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.1">
<l>caṉmam palapala ceytu veḷippaṭṭu caṅkoṭu cakkaramvi</l>
<l>loṇmai yuṭaiya vulakkaiyoḷ vāṭaṇṭu koṇṭupuḷ ḷūrntulakil</l>
<l>vaṉmai yuṭaiya varakka racurarai māḷap paṭaiporuta</l>
<l>naṉmai yuṭaiyavaṉ cīrpara vappeṟṟa nāṉōr kuṟaivilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, who have obtained revering the excellence of him who possesses goodness</l>
<l>who fought with weapons the strong rakṣasas and asuras so they would perish</l>
<l>in the world, mounted on the bird, taking the discus along with the conch, the bow,</l>
<l>a bright pestle, a bright sword [and] a staff, having come out making many many births,</l>
	<l>am without any want.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
